Ur țɛeṭṭel ara daɣen anagar yiwet n tegzirt n Kritus akk-d gma-s, llan gar-asen wid ur numin ara s Lmasiḥ, axaṭer d ikeddaben i llan gar-asen. Leccilen am akken i t-id-ițeffɣen n lekdeb.
?as akken llan gar-asen yergazen n tegzirt n Qubṛus akk-d kra nniḍen n temdint n Qiṛwan, ma d kra n tegzirt n Kritus akk-d wid yumnen s Sidna Ɛisa.
Di yal taswiɛt, sɛut liman am tseddarit s wayes ara tizmirem aț-țsensem isufa n ddunit.
Meɛna m'ara d-ḥyun si ger lmegtin, ad ilin deg-sen ssizdeg imdanen si mkul amkan armi ț-țamurt n Illirya di tmurt n Ibub, win akken i d-yusan ɣuṛ-es mkul ṣṣenf.
A nnger-nwen ay ifariziyen d lɛulama n ccariɛa, ay at sin wudmawen ! Tețɛebbuct s yiwen uɛekkaz iwakken a d-immeslay ɣef wayen yellan țelt n wawal n Sidi Ṛebbi.
?adret iman-nwen ɣef lɛulama n ccariɛa i gḥemmlen ad țḥewwisen s tutlayin nniḍen, neɣ m'ulac ad slen i uselmed n tideț.
Deg anagar wid i d-yusan si tmurt n Maṣer ur neǧhid ara di liman, ț-țarwa n lfeṭṭa, d wid i gellan si mkul amkan ;
Iwexsaṛa : llan azal n ṛebɛa alaf n yemdanen i gumnen s Sidna Ɛisa, yeẓran azal n ṛebɛin iseggasen.
Ur țḍuṛṛut ara lqaɛa d lebḥuṛ neɣ ttjuṛ, alamma neḍbeɛ tiwenziwin n iqeddacen n Ṛebbi Illu-nsen.
Akken kan i d-ṭṭeggiṛent lemwaji timeqqranin tikufta-nsent n lewsex, i d-ssufuɣen nutni tikufta n leɛṛuṛ-nsen.
Ar ass-a qquṛen iqeṛṛay-nwen, qṛib ad yali wass, a ndeggeṛ akkin ɣef yiman-is uqbel a ndeggeṛ akkin fell-as.
?ef wannect-agi i gella d amcafeɛ gar-aɣ d Ṛebbi s yedrimen, neɣ m'ulac kra n wussan, a nerfed leslaḥ s wayes ara ț-țiẓallas, iwakken aț-țaɛekkumt ula ɣef tewwurt.
Walit tigerfiwin , s llebsa ifazen, iwakken ad izdeɣ yid-sen.
Lameɛna atan wayen yeɛnan amdan ur nesɛi lmeɛna, aṭas i gumnen yis.
Deg wannect-agi ilaq aț-țeskker imenɣi akk-d wid iḍaɛen, meɛna ula d nețța i ten-id-ițțaken ṛṛeḥma n Sidi Ṛebbi.
Argaz-agi d țerka, iskker ccwal ger wat Isṛail n ddunit meṛṛa, d nețța i d ameqqran n tejmaɛt n inaṣariyen.
ț-țideț, lumuṛat-agi sselmaden leɛbada, annuz akk-d uɛețțeb n lǧețțat nneɣ, țbanen-d amakken d ayen yelhan, lameɛna d ayen ur nezmir ad iɛawen bunadem ad iṭṭef iman-is.
axaṭer lɛahed-nni n lekdeb i d-ițeffɣen seg waṭas n win akken i t-id yennan : « Lexxal », s wakka i d-ixelqen ayen ur nesɛi azal, tabagust-agi meṛṛa.
Mačči d asmeḥses kan n tmes i gzemren ad fken, meɛna d wid yettabaɛen cci n ddunit meṛṛa ɣer Sidi Ṛebbi i d-ițeffɣen seg imawen-nsen.
