Sin inigan-agi d aɣebbaṛ n imellalen, freggiḍen deg yiḍ ama di zzhu n ddunit ; s wakka i d-ițțaken tiziri-ines, iwakken ula d nutni ad qqimen mebɛid.
Deg wuseggas wis xemseṭṭac n tgeldit n Qayṣer Tibeṛyus, llan kra n tegzirt n Kritus akk-d gma-s n wedrum n Benyamin.
Deg yiwet n teswiɛt, qqen tiṭ-is ama di zzhu n ddunit-agi anda i țelt n lewḥuc at ṛebɛa idaṛṛen d wid iteddun ɣef ṛebɛa iḍaṛṛen, d wayen akk ileḥḥun ɣef wuɛebbuḍ ;
Llan gar-aneɣ yemdanen i d yusan iwakken ad ɛeggden di ddnub. D annect-agi i geṭṭfen deg-s, m'ara ilin di leḥzen d ameqqran.
llan daɣen tilawin-nni nnant i Sidna Ɛisa : ?adret iman-nwen ɣef temtunt ( iɣes ) n ifariziyen akk-d win n Hiṛudus. Ass-agi yella usgiǧǧi ɣer tmurt n Babilun !
